### 인증이 필요한 요청 예시
GET http://localhost:3000/articles
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE


### 1. 자신의 정보 조회
GET http://localhost:3000/users/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### 2. 자신의 정보 수정
PATCH http://localhost:3000/users/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "새로운 닉네임",
  "image": "https://example.com/new-profile.jpg"
}

### 3. 비밀번호 변경
PATCH http://localhost:3000/users/me/password
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "현재비밀번호",
  "newPassword": "새비밀번호123"
}

### 4. 자신이 등록한 상품 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:3000/users/me/products?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### 좋아요 토글
POST http://localhost:3000/likes/products/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### 좋아요한 상품 목록
GET http://localhost:3000/users/me/liked-products
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### 토큰 갱신
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN"
}